items.name: Rough Spool of Thread
items.description: A spool of thread made from fibers. Can be used to make cloth strips.

items.name: Rough Stripped Wood
items.description: Strips of wood taken from a log from a tree. A skilled carpenter could form these into a plank to be used in construction or other crafting recipes.

items.name: Rough Plank
items.description: A plank of wood crafted from stripped wood

items.name: Basic Mushroom
items.description: A plump mushroom that looks edible and quite hearty. Probably better cooked.

items.name: Plain Mushroom Skewer
items.description: Mushrooms roasted on a fire skewered on a stick

items.name: Basic Clay Lump
items.description: A lump of clay. Could be used to build or craft something, or even pave the ground.

items.name: Tree Sap
items.description: A small amount of sticky tree resin

items.name: Pitch
items.description: A sticky material made by processing tree sap in a kiln

items.name: Basic Berry
items.description: A juicy edible berry. Probably better cooked.

items.name: Basic Fertilizer
items.description: A basic fertilizer made at a farming station.

items.name: Training Shortsword
items.description: A flimsy wooden sword. Could be discarded if you could find something better.

items.name: Knapped Flint
items.description: A small shard of flint rock. Brittle but sharp.

items.name: Flint Tool Bundle
items.description: A bundle that contains all the tools you'll need to get started.

items.name: Depleted Automata's Heart
items.description: A depleted Automata's Heart used by Wisp. This heart could be filled with energy to more efficiently power your body.

items.name: Flint Bow
items.description: A bow made from flint.

items.name: Stick
items.description: A regular stick harvested from bushes or striplings. Could be used for crafting or building.

items.name: Basic Flower
items.description: A flower that could be ground up to make pigment or used to make tea

items.name: Basic Pigment
items.description: Pigment made from flowers. Could be used for ink or certain clothing

items.name: Basic Starbulb Plant
items.description: Can be husked into Starlight Onion to get or Starlight Onion Seeds to replant

items.name: Basic Starbulb Seeds
items.description: Can be grown into a Basic Onion Plant in a farming field

items.name: Basic Starbulb
items.description: A Starlight Onion. Maybe a cook could make something good out of this!

items.name: Basic Crop Oil
items.description: Oil made from mashing starbulbs. Could be used to make equipment at a scholar station.

items.name: Plain Roasted Fish
items.description: Filets from a fresh water fish roasted on a fire

items.name: Plain Mashed Bulbs
items.description: Mashed potatoes. Tasty and filling but not overly interesting

items.name: Plain Fish and Bulbs
items.description: Fish arranged in a dish with salty fried potatoes. Delicious and filling

items.name: Plain Berry Pie
items.description: Smells delicious. You can hardly wait to eat it.

items.name: Plain Raw Berry Pie
items.description: An uncooked pie. Bake it in an oven to eat it!

items.name: Rough Wood Log
items.description: A cross section of a tree trunk harvested from trees or fallen trunks. Could be used to build or craft something.

items.name: Rough Wood Trunk
items.description: Can be processed into timber or cut into logs

items.name: Basic Amber Resin
items.description: Pure Resin from a tree. Could be used to make wood polish.

items.name: Rough Tree Bark
items.description: A piece of tree bark. Could be used to make brown or a leatherworking station.

items.name: Basic Citric Berry
items.description: A berry full of citric acid. Could be used by a scholar to make a solvent for refining metal.

items.name: Flint Hammer
items.description: A hammer made from flint

items.name: Flint Chisel
items.description: A chisel made from flint.

items.name: Rough Pebbles
items.description: A handful of tiny pebbles of rock made at a masonry station. Can be used to by masons to make various crafting materials or grinded down to search for gem fragments

items.name: Basic Wood Polish
items.description: Polish that can be used to enhance wood planks. Made by a scholar from Resin and Crop Oil

items.name: Refined Rough Plank
items.description: A plank of wood treated using oil at a carpentry station. Good to make more advanced structures.

items.name: Breezy Fin Darter
items.description: A fish found in the deeper parts of lakes and some rivers. Can provide fish oil, food and also be used as claim for ocean fishing.

items.name: Breezy Fin Darter Filet
items.description: A filet from a fish from the deeper parts of a lake. Could be used to make charm for ocean fishing.

items.name: Basic Fish Oil
items.description: Oil made from fish. Can be used for making leather treatment and ink.

items.name: Wild Fiberplant Seeds
items.description: Can be grown into a domesticated plant which produces filaments

items.name: Basic Wispweave Plant
items.description: Can be used to harvest filament for gathering and Wispweave Seeds to replant

items.name: Basic Wispweave Seeds
items.description: Can be grown into a Wispweave Plant in a farming field. Produces filaments used for making cloth.

items.name: Wild Vegetable Seeds
items.description: Can be turned into white onion seeds by a farmer.

items.name: Wild Grain Seeds
items.description: A wild grain seed. Can be grown into a better crop by farmers.

items.name: Basic Embergrain Plant
items.description: Can be sold, used directly to cook or Embergrain Seeds to replant.

items.name: Basic Embergrain Seeds
items.description: Can be grown into an Embergrain plant in a farming field.

items.name: Plain Mushroom Stuffed Bulbs
items.description: Onions stuffed with wild mushrooms.

items.name: Oceancrest Marlin
items.description: A huge ocean fish. Could be processed into filets, fish oil or scales.

items.name: Oceancrest Marlin Fillet
items.description: A filet from a large ocean fish. Could be used to make food.

items.name: Oceancrest Marlin Scale
items.description: A fish scale crystalized by the salt in the ocean. Various travelers would be interested in this.

items.name: Flint Knife
items.description: A knife made from flint. Requires Leatherworker Lv 1 to equip.

items.name: Flint Hoe
items.description: A hoe made from flint

items.name: Rough Plant Roots
items.description: Massive plant roots that could be processed into plant fiber at a forager's workstation

items.name: Rough Plant Fiber
items.description: A strong piece of plant fiber. Could be used to build or craft something

items.name: Rough Glass Vial
items.description: A vial that could be filled with solvents or elixirs

items.name: Plain Cooked Berries
items.description: Berries that have been cooked into a mushy mess. Tasty enough though.

items.name: Crushed Rough Shells
items.description: Ground sea shells. Can be used by a mason to make more refined bricks.

items.name: Rough Gypsite
items.description: A rare mineral found in clay. Can be used to make more refined bricks.

items.name: Basic Firesand
items.description: Various stone materials ground, boiled and baked by a cook. Can be used to refine bricks.

items.name: Basic Ink
items.description: Ink made of pigment and fish oil. Could be used by a scholar to transcribe some sayings found in hieroglyphs around the world and in ruins.

items.name: Basic Embergrain Dough
items.description: A dough ball made of Embergrain Flour

items.name: Flint Pickaxe
items.description: A pickaxe made from flint.

items.name: Flint Machete
items.description: A machete made from flint.

items.name: Rough Stone Chunk
items.description: Can be used in construction or refined into a block

items.name: Rough Braxite
items.description: A rare abrasive stone that can be used to make a leather finish solution to refine leather

items.name: Rough Wispweave Filament
items.description: A finer cloth filament that could be used to make cloth. Grown by farmers.

items.name: Rough Cloth Strip
items.description: Could be sewed into either Rope or Cloth by a skilled tailor.

items.name: Rough Cloth
items.description: A thick weave of cloth made by a tailor.

items.name: Moonlit Crawdad
items.description: A fish found in shallow lakes and rivers. Can be used to cook food or as bait and a source of shells.

items.name: Basic Bait
items.description: Bait made of a dried fish. Could be used to catch larger fish.

items.name: Basic Embergrain
items.description: Embergrains which could be cooked into dough

items.name: Flint Quill
items.description: A quill made from flint.

items.name: Flint Rod
items.description: A fishing rod made from flint.

items.name: Ferralith Ore Concentrate
items.description: Ore that's been processed into a fine concentrate. Could be smelted into metal.

items.name: Molten Ferralith
items.description: A bar of molten metal made by smelting concentrate.

items.name: Rough Rope
items.description: A thick rope made out of multiple strands of cordage. Could be used for crafting or building.

items.name: Water Bucket
items.description: A bucket full of fresh water

items.name: Flint Saw
items.description: A saw made from flint.

items.name: Flint Scissors
items.description: A pair of scissors made from flint.

items.name: Plain Skewered Baitfish
items.description: Small fish skewered on a stick and cooked on a fire

items.name: Basic Raw Meat
items.description: A piece of meat from a wild animal. Could be used as a cooking ingredient.

items.name: Basic Chum
items.description: Can be used to chum fishing nodes in the ocean. Once chummed, nodes remain fishable for 15 minutes.

items.name: Flint Axe
items.description: An axe made from flint.

items.name: Breezy Darter Filet
items.description: A filet from a fish from the deeper parts of a lake. Could be used for food or to make chum for ocean fishing.

items.name: Basic Food Waste
items.description: Discarded scraps of food. Can be used to create fertilizer.

items.name: Sagi Bird
items.description: An animal body that could be processed for meat and hides

items.name: Rough Animal Hair
items.description: A particularly strong hair from an animal. This could be used to make more refined cloth.

items.name: Rough Raw Pelt
items.description: A fresh pelt from a wild animal. Could be cleaned at a leatherworking station for use.

items.name: Salt
items.description: Sea salt. Could be used to cook something tasty.

items.name: Empty Bucket
items.description: An empty wood bucket, could be filled with water from a well

items.name: Simple Fertilizer
items.description: A more advanced type of fertilizer made at a farming station. Used to fertilize better crops.

items.name: Simple Wispweave Plant
items.description: Can be split into Wispweave Filament for tailoring and Wispweave Seeds to replant.

items.name: Simple Starbulb Plant
items.description: Can be hooked into Starlight Onions to eat or Starlight Onion Seeds to replant

items.name: Simple Embergrain Plant
items.description: Can be split into Embergrain to cook or Embergrain Seeds to replant

items.name: Plain Roasted Meat
items.description: Meat cooked on an open fire

items.name: Rough Cleaned Pelt
items.description: A hide that has been cleaned and prepared for use. Can be used to make leather at a tanning station.

items.name: Basic Tannin
items.description: A material made from processing water and bark in a tanning tub. Used to tan leather.

items.name: Rough Tanned Pelt
items.description: A tanned pelt that could be turned into leather at a leatherworking station.
